project_descr: A Groundwork to Zero: Improving Response to HIV Prevention among Men Who Have Sex with Men (MSM) and Transgenders (TG) by Developing National HIV Prevention Guidelines among MSM and TG and Supporting Municipal-level Implementation

outputs.output_descr:
National guidelines on HIV prevention among men having sex with men and transgender people in Thailand is finalized and approved.

Local-level implementation of national guideline HIV Prevetion among men having sex with men and transgender people in Thailand is in place

project_title: a groundwork to zero: national guidelines for msm/tg
